-- Dollar. Euro Share of Global Reserves Declined in First Quarter, IMF Says
-- Sandrine Rastello
-- 2010-06-30T14:15:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/dollar-euro-share-of-global-reserves-declined-in-first-quarter-imf-says.html

          
          
             (Corrects prior percentages to account for revisions.)  
 The U.S. dollar’s share of global
currency reserves fell to 61.5 percent in the first quarter this
year from 62.2 percent the previous quarter, and the euro’s
share fell to 27.2 percent from 27.3 percent, the International
Monetary Fund said today in a quarterly report.  
